query:
SELECT 
  productId, partNumber, brand, name, description, category, series,
  particleSize, poreSize, columnLength, innerDiameter, phaseType,
  phMin, phMax, status, imageUrl
FROM products
WHERE status = 'active'
LIMIT 10;
